{"tid":2456904,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大馬女神沒有人敢追？林明禎：肥肚腩很性感　姐弟戀也OK","createTime":"2021-03-22T09:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T01:44:30.000Z","uid":9573,"like":18,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5a10731f39131daa2dcf35400df1ce2572045a98","tid":2456904,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"「大馬女神」林明禎同時也有「真人版娜美」的稱號，有著天使般的臉孔與惹火身材的她，受到網友們深深吸引，社群網站IG追蹤數多達接近112萬。先前林明禎因為「野外瑜伽」影片疑似「下身現形」而刪文一事，港媒訪問她時表示十分無言：「我原意是想鼓勵大家多做運動，沒想過有些人就是會看到奇怪的事。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cfcdn.she.com/media/she.com/2020/09/511005-511005-%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2020-09-18-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.43.40.jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcfcdn.she.com%2Fmedia%2Fshe.com%2F2020%2F09%2F511005-511005-%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2020-09-18-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258811.43.40.jpg.jpg&h=54d29756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「大馬女神」林明禎開始在台灣為工作根據地。<br />\n<br />\n林明禎現在正式以台灣為演藝根據地，除去年拍攝港片《一秒拳王》及其他各地的工作，必須飛來飛去外，上周末在新竹體育館為職籃聯盟P. LEAGUE+，為攻城獅進行開場表演情歌《T.O.U》更擔任應援，吸引不少粉絲到場，然而大家也關心她的感情狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.moedict.tw/%E9%87%8D%E8%A4%87.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moedict.tw%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A4%2587.png&h=4f11ce21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林明禎大方露出蠻腰讓許多粉絲重複觀看多次。<br />\n<br />\n林明禎聊到自己擇偶條件，她覺得年紀與外表並不是她考慮的重要，現在不排除姐弟戀，她坦言曾交過外表不是特別出眾的男友，包括， 般奴費南迪斯、麥湯米尼、勞基梳爾及卡雲尼，她認為這是一種磁場。更表示光頭的男生也可以很帥、有肚腩的男生可以很性感「像光頭的美國影星巨石強森就很帥，所以並不排斥光頭或肚腩的男生交往。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12551549020/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F12551549020%2F641&h=82fc0d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林明禎自嘆近期沒人敢追。<br />\n<br />\n不過現實中，今年30歲的林明禎，自嘆暫時沒有追求者追她，李斯特城再在78分鐘由伊恩拿祖頂入，將勝局鎖定贏3:1，讓她感到十分可惜。去年花了不少時間在居家隔離上，為了拍戲與各地的工作必須飛來飛去，去年光因隔離就花了高達70多天，害她沒有機會給人追。"},{"pid":"f3b643b30bc7442ee0fa3d5a09942cfad11efbf5","tid":2456904,"uid":146556,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"...... 做乜撚嘢"},{"pid":"3a0af99c879756b59d7f9957ef28b837d92dcd56","tid":2456904,"uid":6842,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"她坦言曾交過外表不是特別出眾的男友，包括， 般奴費南迪斯、麥湯米尼、勞基梳爾及卡雲尼，她認為這是一種磁場。<br />\n<br />\n李斯特城再在78分鐘由伊恩拿祖頂入，將勝局鎖定贏3:1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc255cadbbe44d2a7460415d6daff4a35b4c5d17","tid":2456904,"uid":58201,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"第一張圖朱千雪嚟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc19f1c83fb186bb591dc402c4fd29f06e0d66fe","tid":2456904,"uid":161988,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:06:04.000Z","msg":"？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？"},{"pid":"9c7b01c743eb9fff3ed5cc7284b2f5c78a31786f","tid":2456904,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:06:13.000Z","msg":"乜鳩野post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab6a1c51918e3240e47ccf45e4d29b9e38eb506","tid":2456904,"uid":1874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20